    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Step 2: Create Variant\n\n**Instructions:**\n1. Select your template from the dropdown\n2. Click \"Add Layer Override\"\n3. Select a layer to customize\n4. Add override values (text, image URL, etc.)\n5. Execute to create your variant image!\n\n**Example overrides:**\n- Text layer: Change the text content\n- Image layer: Set a new image URL\n- Any layer: Adjust color, position, size",
        "height": 328,
        "width": 340,
